<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Estética Carletti | Spa</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Inter:wght@200;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = { theme: { extend: { colors: { gold: '#d4af37', darkBody: '#0c0a09', darkCard: '#141210' }, fontFamily: { serif: ['Cormorant Garamond', 'serif'], sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'] } } } }
    </script>
    <style>body { background-color: #0c0a09; color: #e7e5e4; } .service-card { border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1); background: #141210; transition: 0.4s; } .service-card:hover { border-color: #d4af37; transform: translateY(-5px); }</style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-darkBody/95 border-b border-white/5 h-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-full flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-gold italic text-xl">C</div>
                <h1 class="text-sm font-serif tracking-widest uppercase text-gold">Estética Carletti</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
                <a href="../index.html" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-gold">Facial</a>
                <a href="../corporal/index.html" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-gold">Corporal</a>
                <a href="index.html" class="text-gold border-b border-gold">Spa</a>
                <a href="../depilacao/index.html" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-gold">Depilação</a>
            </div>
            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-gold text-black text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded-full">Agendar</button>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center px-6">
        <div class="absolute inset-0"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?q=80&w=2070" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-darkBody via-darkBody/80 to-transparent"></div></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full pt-20">
            <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif mb-6 leading-tight">Ritual <br><span class="italic text-gold">de SPA</span></h2>
            <p class="max-w-md text-stone-400 font-light text-lg italic">Desconecte-se do mundo. Reconecte-se com você.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Banho de Ouro</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Hidratação e brilho extremo.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Pedras Quentes</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Terapia térmica relaxante.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Candle Massage</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Massagem com velas aromáticas.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Escalda Pés</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Alívio e boas-vindas.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Argiloterapia</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Nutrição mineral profunda.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Spa dos Pés</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Cuidado e maciez absoluta.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Massagem Crânio</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Alívio total de tensões.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Esfoliação Marinha</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Pele renovada e suave.</p></div>
        <div class="service-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center"><h4 class="text-white font-serif text-lg uppercase mb-2">Day Spa VIP</h4><p class="text-[11px] text-stone-500">Experiência completa Carletti.</p></div>
    </section>
    <footer class="py-20 text-center border-t border-white/5"><button class="px-12 py-5 bg-gold text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] rounded-full">Reservar Experiência</button></footer>
    <script>lucide.createIcons();</script>
</body>
</html>
